Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.47,0:01:41.47,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.47,0:01:42.50,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.50,0:01:44.88,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This huge amount of snow is troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.88,0:01:49.48,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially on the day Headquarters says that we have to patrol carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.66,0:01:56.09,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't given up on Jakotto-san, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.09,0:01:58.24,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not really like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.24,0:02:00.15,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, ain't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.15,0:02:01.85,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been searching and searching.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:06.02,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can't even find her after this much effort, we should just believe in "maybe".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.55,0:02:10.44,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.88,0:02:15.73,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling that Kureha-chan is a little bit like Rio-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.51,0:02:28.01,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.01,0:02:31.06,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Beneath the mountain, at 11 o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.06,0:02:32.67,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,About 400 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.29,0:02:52.01,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, please wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:02:57.66,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even her clothes are frozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.66,0:02:59.87,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, take off your coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:02.19,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We are changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.54,0:03:05.99,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:10.50,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A Roman soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:36.78,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You really can restore this machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:40.66,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder you are one of the most talented girls in the academy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:43.82,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This way, we can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.17,0:03:46.06,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:47.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kannagi Noël-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.38,0:03:54.75,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.02,0:04:02.63,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They found her while they were patrolling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.63,0:04:03.88,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Roman soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.17,0:04:07.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she broke her left leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:14.28,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, her fingers are turning dark-red!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:17.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's frostbitten.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.58,0:04:20.95,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're not careful, she might even lose her fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:28.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}The Witch of Helvetia...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:34.92,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:46.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like it's going to be okay somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.54,0:04:48.45,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Her fingers are alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.45,0:04:49.76,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.16,0:04:51.26,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How about Noël-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.96,0:04:54.57,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She said that she would be with her for some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.57,0:04:56.02,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:59.15,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's trying really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:02.15,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She looked as if she was repairing the Takemicaduchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:04.15,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.19,0:05:11.33,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Trumpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:14.94,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Will she be successful, in the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:18.63,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:20.25,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.39,0:05:24.82,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody ever expected to find a Roman soldier in such a place...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:26.41,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.41,0:05:29.42,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my first time meeting a Roman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.42,0:05:31.89,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're enemies, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.22,0:05:37.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, when thinking about those people that look like demons...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.58,0:05:41.77,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we are seen the same way in Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:44.65,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.06,0:05:50.16,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After seeing that girl,  I thought that Roman people are the same as us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:53.19,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kanata! What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.19,0:05:54.16,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Kana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:57.41,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about the end of your shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.95,0:06:08.72,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still a lot of trouble going on at the peace conference, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:10.51,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that it's like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:14.17,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to submit a report about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.17,0:06:19.74,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I do that, the girl's likely to be taken to Central for interrogation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:25.82,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to do this! Under such an unstable situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:28.80,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's invading the enemy's territory!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.80,0:06:31.05,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As a soldier, she's ready for torture...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.14,0:06:31.07,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an "interrogation."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:38.62,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be the one to decide how she's gonna be treated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:43.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, give me some time, Kureha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.83,0:06:51.70,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't forget that we are soldiers, Platoon Leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.38,0:07:02.42,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just listen to my words for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:06.43,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When you carried that girl here, did you meet anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:11.24,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. I was focused on carrying her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.92,0:07:13.19,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.19,0:07:14.24,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:36.78,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio, how would you deal with this problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:21.06,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\i1}A Helvetian soldier...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.75,0:08:32.69,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.13,0:08:43.12,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:45.33,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}Am I a Helvetian prisoner?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.97,0:08:50.14,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't speak Roman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.14,0:08:50.85,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.85,0:08:52.34,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}So you took me prisoner—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:57.34,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that scream just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:08:58.70,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.63,0:09:02.77,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She... woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.37,0:09:05.39,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.44,0:09:18.46,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}Imperial Roman Army, First Armored Division, 13th Battalion B-Company.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.46,0:09:24.75,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}Sergeant Major Aisha Ardora, serial number 1031021.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.19,0:09:27.34,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.34,0:09:31.50,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}Imperial Roman Army, Sergeant Major Aisha Ardora.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:33.00,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,0:09:37.02,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}Serial number 1031021.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:41.85,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, how dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.99,0:09:46.10,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How's it going? Have you got a clue?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:47.60,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's totally impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.95,0:09:51.04,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that she doesn't understand Helvetian.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.04,0:09:55.66,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All we know is her Serial Number and her name, "Aisha".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.08,0:10:01.68,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Second Lieutenant Felicia Heideman who's in charge of this fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:08.12,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have such great breasts. I'm interested in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:12.22,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I suck or rub them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.22,0:10:14.63,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I play with your body?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.91,0:10:20.99,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-What are you saying, Platoon leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:25.39,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that she really doesn't understand Helvetian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:28.39,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, that's bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:30.39,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't interrogate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.26,0:10:34.90,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We must find someone who can speak Roman as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:36.93,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.93,0:10:43.48,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we can interrogate her and make a preliminary report, our platoon is to protect this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.48,0:10:44.63,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.07,0:10:48.91,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to place a bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.95,0:10:52.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't hear anything, so the result is not on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.76,0:10:58.29,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisha-chan, welcome to the Time telling fortress!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.29,0:11:00.47,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}Ti-me-tell-ing-for-tress?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:01.17,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.17,0:11:02.93,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Time telling fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:06.79,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}Ah, I see... Then I made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.32,0:11:09.60,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}Grandmother...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:30.76,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, is it too hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.24,0:11:50.10,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She ate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.30,0:11:52.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tastes okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:56.36,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}To escape, I need strength, so I'll eat your food.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.39,0:11:59.66,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She must be saying that it tastes great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.84,0:12:03.34,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What on Earth is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.34,0:12:05.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata might be doing what she usually does but,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:07.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,why is Noël also being so nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.04,0:12:10.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's atonement for her sins, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:18.04,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}Have you ever seen the fossil of an angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.04,0:12:20.26,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:27.13,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}They don't understand me, I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.67,0:12:30.71,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Roman. I wish I'd studied it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.71,0:12:31.98,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:34.36,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we could communicate with her using the language, we could...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:39.79,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for you work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.79,0:12:41.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Yumina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:44.34,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have enough people to shovel the snow at the church?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.34,0:12:45.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:48.33,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The kids are working really seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:49.83,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.26,0:12:53.33,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, they won't be kids forever, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:55.15,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:13:03.12,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Human beings grow every day, like the sound of Kanata-san's trumpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:07.45,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were Rio, I guess she would say "that's not good enough."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.45,0:13:11.64,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, nee-san, aren't you stocking things in Treize?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:15.07,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of things happened, and it turned out to be useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.53,0:13:17.56,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:20.86,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, about the fortress...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.29,0:13:24.36,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about something bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.21,0:13:28.96,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:30.83,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}It's a wonderful melody.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.75,0:13:35.51,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}Ah, I didn't know there were trumpets like that left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:39.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.14,0:13:41.09,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:43.84,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I think Rio-senpai would allow it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:05.86,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}It's a good trumpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.21,0:14:07.97,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\pos(640,635)}Really, I haven't seen one this nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:10.15,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, the music you just played was so great!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.15,0:14:11.87,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:14.87,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I heard that from Iliya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.17,0:14:17.66,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio-senpai heard the same music too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:22.86,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The same music is heard, not only in Helvetia, but in Rome too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.19,0:14:27.13,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Music really is heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.04,0:14:31.43,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,in both Rome and Helvetia, in the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.21,0:14:46.80,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Temporary measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.13,0:14:59.39,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}Danke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.39,0:15:00.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dan...ke?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:02.47,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}Yeah, danke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.47,0:15:04.84,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's "danke"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:06.50,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It means "Thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:12.36,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, things are getting out of hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.04,0:15:16.55,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this town hasn't become a target of the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.15,0:15:21.78,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we include parents, sisters, brothers and all other relatives,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.78,0:15:25.96,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then almost all of the people living here have lost someone in the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:29.64,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's always like that. Even those nice people would, when it happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:34.97,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Migel, the one who runs the pub. Remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.94,0:15:40.30,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I even went to his place yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.22,0:15:45.17,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that the Helvetian military is doing a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.97,0:15:48.02,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They are moving toward this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:55.78,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's related to the appearance of this Roman soldier in such a remote place, it's serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.04,0:16:01.89,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we have to ask this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:03.44,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Naomi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:07.36,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know anyone who understands Roman?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.44,0:16:10.46,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I sure do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:18.16,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}I am Yumina.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:22.66,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}I am a servant of the Helvetian Orthodox Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:25.52,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}May the blessings of the all be upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.55,0:16:27.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.32,0:16:28.84,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}One of these kittens!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:33.34,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}There's only one God, that greeting is blasphemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:35.37,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is she saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:37.55,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just saying hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:40.13,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't waste time on that! Please ask her now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:42.59,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:49.77,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}If you don't tell us, you put everyone here in a very bad position.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.35,0:16:56.66,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}If you feel any sort of obligation to them, then tell us the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.97,0:17:09.57,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}I can't tell you about my mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.57,0:17:14.13,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}But I wanted to see the Angel Fossil located in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.75,0:17:18.72,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She says that she's doing this to see the Angel fossil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.02,0:17:20.59,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel fossil?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.59,0:17:21.72,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:29.65,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}My grandmother was a Maiden here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.30,0:17:33.48,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My grandma was a soldier of the time telling fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.48,0:17:36.68,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}She was captured at the Eastern Front and met my grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.68,0:17:40.11,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She was captured on the eastern battle line, and met my grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.11,0:17:43.03,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}As I grew up, I listened to her stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.03,0:17:45.50,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I listened to her stories while growing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.42,0:17:52.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}So I wanted to see the Angel of the apocalypse that brought judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.61,0:17:57.65,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}to the world in the distant past, the one my grandmother spoke of.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.52,0:18:00.57,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not telling the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.57,0:18:02.96,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who destroyed the world was the devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.96,0:18:06.10,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. Please translate correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:12.94,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see the Angel of the apocalypse who destroyed the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.79,0:18:15.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.77,0:18:20.98,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That melody... The marching trumpet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.55,0:18:28.91,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ninth Independent Task Force of the First Imperial Guards!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.91,0:18:32.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ninth? Isn't it Colonel Hopkins'?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:35.00,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the one you dreamt about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.38,0:18:38.42,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one's who's called "the God of Vingt."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:44.47,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He revived the weapons from the past, and is said to have destroyed three towns in one night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:49.43,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.99,0:18:52.56,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't know that you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:54.08,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,0:18:55.68,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.68,0:18:58.07,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you have time to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:19:02.19,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't make a decision as soon as possible, you will get into trouble, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.19,0:19:03.60,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To hand over that girl, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.38,0:19:05.24,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have to worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.64,0:19:08.26,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We are soldiers of Helvetia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.19,0:19:11.39,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost this gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.39,0:19:13.79,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't make it in time, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:15.75,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.28,0:19:20.41,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio-senpai said that she didn't want anyone to suffer misfortune anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.41,0:19:23.01,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She said that's why she's doing what she can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:25.91,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she left, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.73,0:19:30.09,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.04,0:19:34.43,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We are the same, we are together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.36,0:19:40.15,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As the leader of Platoon 1121, I command.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.63,0:19:48.74,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This order is based on my own judgement. I announce my responsibility for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.97,0:19:51.91,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we all in agreement?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.28,0:20:06.18,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Second Lieutenant Felicia Heideman, the Leader of Platoon 1121.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.44,0:20:10.10,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A scout of the Roman military was captured in Treize.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.39,0:20:16.41,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, during the interrogation, there was an accident, so we don't know the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:22.62,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How surprising! There's also information saying that there's a Roman soldier in Seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.39,0:20:24.86,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You got a clue?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.39,0:20:27.37,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.09,0:20:29.49,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.52,0:20:37.71,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At this time, Fortress 1121 will be taken over by us, The Ninth Independent Task Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.64,0:20:49.09,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make such a big noise so suddenly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.09,0:20:50.73,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.73,0:20:55.39,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisha-san is asking me about the tale of the Maidens of Flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.96,0:20:58.27,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange. What she says is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.53,0:21:01.98,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Search everywhere thoroughly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:03.33,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This way too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.99,0:21:04.94,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How about there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.94,0:21:06.19,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Negative here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.19,0:21:07.27,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We must find her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.27,0:21:08.78,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Open that door!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.67,0:21:12.17,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She has to be somewhere. Watch the entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.10,0:21:25.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She said "by the way, I still don't know your name."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.58,0:21:26.17,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.64,0:21:28.39,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}Her name is Noël.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.35,0:21:32.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}Noël... Noël Kannagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.80,0:21:33.63,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.19,0:21:35.67,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}The Witch of Helvetia...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.67,0:21:37.24,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\}The Invisible God of death...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.88,0:21:40.23,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You said the invisible God of death!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.08,0:21:51.87,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, is that a mouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.90,0:21:53.70,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.46,0:22:12.39,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hello. This is Fortress 1121.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.88,0:22:20.44,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In Nomansland, at Seize's border, there's a big Roman troop!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.44,0:22:22.44,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,
